title: Kerala tattoo artist Sujeesh held after multiple women allege sexual assault - The News Minute

description: Sujeesh PS, a Kochi-based tattoo artist accused of sexually abusing multiple women, was arrested by the Kerala police on Saturday, February 5. Earlier in the day, the police had filed two First Information Reports (FIR) against Sujeesh, after six women approached the Commissioner of Police in this regard. Sujeesh, who was on the run ever since the issue came out, was arrested by the Kochi city police team while he was trying to reach the office of an advocate on Saturday night.
